@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_krdrkx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.85 - v0 + 0.48)) + wp.cos(0.61))
    v0 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.46 / v0 + 0.57) * (v0 + 0.51 - v1 + 0.19)))
    v0 = (0.97 + v2)
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
